text: Ah the ramblers must do a roaring trade.
I've been trying to get hold of him
to organize meat for the barbecue.
When is the barbecue, the twentieth?
--That was the day I was thinking of having a proper lunch party but I won't do it if you're going out.
No, I haven't I won't have finished my reports then.
(()) two weekends away I shall be up my to ears in it  --
